altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 25
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 25
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v25 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Virtua Quest, Mario Power Tennis, Donkey Kong Jungle Beat, Star Fox: Assault, and Metroid Prime 2: Echoes. The disc also features trailers of the following: Donkey Kong Jungle Beat, NBA Street V3, Star Fox: Assault, Dragon Ball Z: Sagas, NFL Street 2, the Nintendo DS, and an ESRB ratings video.
